">Саудовская Аравия</span></a></span>&#160;— <a href="https://ru.wikipedia.org/wiki/%D0%94%D0%B5%D0%BD%D1%8C_%D0%BD%D0%B5%D0%B7%D0%B0%D0%B2%D0%B8%D1%81%D0%B8%D0%BC%D0%BE%D1%81%D1%82%D0%B8" title="День независимости">День независимости</a> (от Великобритании, <a href="https://ru.wikipedia.org/wiki/1927" class="mw-redirect" title="1927">1927</a>).</li><li><span style="display: none; speak: none;" class="noprint">Украина</span><span style="white-space:nowrap;"><span class="flagicon"><a href="https://ru.wikipedia.org/wiki/%D0%A3%D0%BA%D1%80%D0%B0%D0%B8%D0%BD%D0%B0" title="Украина"><img alt="Flag of Ukraine.svg" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/49/Flag_of_Ukraine.svg/22px-Flag_of_Ukraine.svg.png" width="22" height="15" class="thumbborder" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/49/Flag_of_Ukraine.svg/33px-Flag_of_Ukraine.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/49/Flag_of_Ukraine.svg/44px-Flag_of_Ukraine.svg.png 2x" data-file-width="1200" data-file-height="800" /></a></span>&#160;<a href="https://ru.wikipedia.org/wiki/%D0%A3%D0%BA%D1%80%D0%B0%D0%B8%D0%BD%D0%B0" title="Украина"><span style="white-space: normal;">Украина</span></a></span>&#160;— <a href="https://ru.wikipedia.org/wiki/%D0%94%D0%B5%D0%BD%D1%8C_%D0%B1%D0%B0%D0%BD%D0%BA%D0%BE%D0%B2%D1%81%D0%BA%D0%B8%D1%85_%D1%80%D0%B0%D0%B1%D0%BE%D1%82%D0%BD%D0%B8%D0%BA%D0%BE%D0%B2_%D0%A3%D0%BA%D1%80%D0%B0%D0%B8%D0%BD%D1%8B" title="День банковских работников Украины">День банковских работников</a>.</li></ul><h3><span class="mw-headline" id=".D0.A0.D0.B5.D0.BB.D0.B8.D0.B3.D0.B8.D0.BE.D0.B7.D0.BD.D1.8B.D0.B5"><a href="https://ru.wikipedia.org/wiki/%D0%A4%D0%B0%D0%B9%D0%BB:P_religion_world.svg" class="image"><img alt="P religion world.svg" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/28/P_religion_world.svg/30px-P_religion_world.svg.png" width="30" height="27" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/28/P_religion_world.svg/45px-P_religion_world.